{"tid":1212439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有人搞地鐵會影響到大眾同政府？","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:28:45.000Z","uid":1121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92230b4ae0f54095ced27c396db3b7710839792a","tid":1212439,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:40:48.000Z","msg":"2018-12-20 00:22:40<br />\n港鐵今年10月16日早上繁忙時間發生四線故障，港鐵今日應政府要求提交調查報告，交代事故原因和日後應變安排。報告提及，事故主因是基於荃灣線、港島線、觀塘線、將軍澳線四條線，由兩個不同系統的軟件計數器聯繫，事發兩者的重置安排不一致，而前線維修人員從不知悉兩個系統有不匹配的地方，引致故障發生。<br />\n<br />\n結果：香港人遲少少都係番工，政府冇事發生，地鐵罰八百萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵列車相撞事件於2019年3月18日凌晨約2時45分在香港發生，當時港鐵兩列不載客列車在荃灣綫及金鐘站之間的「交叉渡線」道岔相撞。<br />\n<br />\n結果：停三日，香港人遲少少轉多程車都係番工，政府冇事發生，地鐵罰2500萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果搞停地鐵係社會行動，咁地鐵一定係社運組織<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7fb5742281a524d0017ab75287c6cf08c9f887","tid":1212439,"uid":22894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:43:03.000Z","msg":"呢個係來自一班鐵膠嘅呼籲<br />\n搭車要摸清楚緊急設備 免得出起事來累人累己<br />\n拿 唔係緊急唔好用呀 一個唔該半個鐘都無車到<br />\n影響大家翻工就麻鳩煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHPEtk5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHPEtk5.png&h=e0650ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs39Qzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs39Qzu.png&h=3d5a172e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNetmF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNetmF8.png&h=6a8ffb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0qwjsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0qwjsM.png&h=ddd4ac0a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90M7Cew.pn